Node API
-------------------------
To debug:
Using Chrome, go to http://[ApiHostAddress]/app/api.js/debug. In the local environment this would be:
http://reciperepoapi.dev.local/app/api.js/debug/

Node unit tests
-------------------------
To run tests:
mocha .\test\**\*.js

To debug tests:
node-debug -p 8090 _mocha .\test\**\*.js --no-timeouts

Node integration tests
-------------------------
To run tests:
mocha .\integration-test\**\*.js

To debug tests:
node-debug -p 8090 _mocha .\integration-test\**\*.js --no-timeouts